  EffectDiscription_JPN: 
  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Digivolve][DoruGreymon]: Cost 1 \n\n[Trash] [All Turns]
    When one of your [DoruGreymon] would be deleted, by digivolving it into this
    card without paying the cost, prevent that deletion.\n[When Digivolving] Trash
    1 card in your hand. Then, \uFF1CDraw 1\uFF1E. If [DoruGreymon] is in this Digimon's
    digivolution cards or this digivolved from the trash, delete 1 of your opponent's
    Digimon with a play cost of 6 or less instead."
